Author: BigBob-omb91
Text: You can make an ok spaghetti substitute with shiritaki noodles. A large portion of those noodles is like 25 calories. Pair it with a 1/2 cup marinara (45cals, I have seen some higher calorie versions so make sure you check!) and you have a big bowl of spaghetti for around 70 calories.

Author: silkirishroses
Text: When my dad makes spaghetti I literally just eat the turkey meatballs and try not to say anything when my sister wonders where all the meat went.
